#

Beef Borshch

140 min
$15
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

Ukrainian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

soupheartycomfort food

Description

A hearty and comforting Ukrainian beet soup, packed with flavor and nutrients.

Ingredients

  • beef (chuck or brisket): 1 lb
  • beets: 2 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 1 large, grated
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • tomato paste: 2 tbsp
  • beef broth: 6 cups
  • bay leaves: 2
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • sour cream: for serving
